name: <core_simd::vector::Simd<*const T, N> as core_simd::simd::ptr::const_ptr::SimdConstPtr>::expose_provenance

intrinsics::simd::simd_expose_provenance.doc:
Exposes a vector of pointers as a vector of addresses.

 `T` must be a vector of pointers.

 `U` must be a vector of `usize` with the same length as `T`.
